<div id="wikihead"><h2><a href="http://rephial.org/wiki/UserManual">UserManual</a> &gt; StatusCodes</h2></div>

<div id="wikicontent"><div class="page"><h4 id="s2_1">Monster status</h4><p>The colour information for the monster damage status is:<ul><li>Green: Unhurt<li>Yellow: Slightly wounded<li>Orange: Wounded<li>Red: Badly wounded<li>Dark Red: Almost dead</ul><ul><li>Dark Blue: Asleep<li>Bright Blue: Stunned<li>Brown: Confused<li>Purple: Afraid</ul><p>Monsters are often asleep when discovered, and the better your character&#39;s stealth, the better the chances they stay that way while a character sneaks up on them.<p>Monsters can become confused, like characters, due to magical attacks.<p>Stunning can also be due to attacks or spells, as for characters.<p>Monsters become afraid when severely wounded - i.e. close to death, or when dealt a single massive blow.</div><hr /><div class="page"><h4 id="s2_2">Wounds</h4><p>These are, progressively:<ul><li>Graze (yellow text)<li>Light Cut (yellow)<li>Bad Cut (orange)<li>Nasty Cut (orange)<li>Severe Cut (red)<li>Deep Gash<li>Mortal Wound</ul></div><hr /><div class="page"><h4 id="s2_3">Hunger</h4><p>The progression of Hunger flags is as follows:<ul><li>Gorged (dark green text)<li>Full (green)<li>(blank)<li>Hungry (yellow)<li>Weak (orange)<li>Weak (red)</ul></div><hr /><div class="page"><h4 id="s2_4">Level Feelings (old)</h4><ul><li>What a boring place...<li>This level can&#39;t be all bad...<li>You like the look of this place...<li>You feel your luck is turning...<li>You feel strangely lucky...<li>You have a good feeling...<li>You have a very good feeling...<li>You have an excellent feeling...<li>You have a superb feeling about this level</ul></div><hr /><div class="page"><h4 id="s2_5">Level Feelings (new)</h4><ul><li>Looks like any other level. (not enough time)<li>This place looks uninteresting.<li>This seems a quiet, peaceful place.<li>This place seems reasonably safe.<li>You are unsure about this place.<li>You feel a little lucky.<li>You have a good feeling...<li>You have a very good feeling...<li>You have an excellent feeling...<li>You have a superb feeling about this level.<li>You feel there is something special here...</ul></div></div>

